Package: lantern
Type: Package
Title: Ancestry-Specific Rare Variant Association Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Yu",
           family = "Wang",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "wangyu19940804@gmail.com")
Description: Ancestry-specific rare variant burden testing for admixed
    populations. Uses a pure C backend to split genotype dosages by local
    ancestry inferred from phased or unphased data, then runs
    ancestry-stratified SMMAT gene-level tests via GMMAT.
